msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "Eksempler:"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"In your CMP, block the BimBeau Privacy Analytics advanced stats script until "
"the Statistics or Analytics purpose is accepted."
msgstr ""
"I din CMP skal du blokere BimBeau Privacy Analytics-scriptet til avanceret "
"statistik, indtil formålet Statistik eller Analyse er accepteret."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Advanced stats are disabled. BimBeau Privacy Analytics will only use "
"essential stats."
msgstr ""
"Avanceret statistik er deaktiveret. BimBeau Privacy Analytics bruger kun "
"essentiel statistik."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Respect DNT / GPC"
msgstr "Respektér DNT / GPC"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Stop measurement when the visitor’s browser sends a Do Not Track or Global "
"Privacy Control signal."
msgstr ""
"Stop måling, når den besøgendes browser sender et Do Not Track- eller Global "
"Privacy Control-signal."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Visit measurement"
msgstr "Besøgsmåling"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Defines how long visitor activity can remain grouped under the same visitor "
"row before a new row is started after inactivity."
msgstr ""
"Definerer, hvor længe besøgsaktivitet kan forblive grupperet under den samme "
"besøgsrække, før en ny række startes efter inaktivitet."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid "Visitor activity window"
msgstr "Aktivitetsvindue for besøgende"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Defines how long activity from the same visitor can remain grouped into one "
"visitor row. After this period of inactivity, BimBeau Privacy Analytics "
"starts a new visitor row. Range: 300 to 86400 seconds (5 minutes to 24 "
"hours)."
msgstr ""
"Definerer, hvor længe aktivitet fra den samme besøgende kan forblive "
"grupperet i én besøgsrække. Efter denne periode med inaktivitet starter "
"BimBeau Privacy Analytics en ny besøgsrække. Interval: 300 til 86400 "
"sekunder (5 minutter til 24 timer)."

